OL,5, Former Wales rugby captain Gareth      
OL,6, Thomas has settled a legal dispute with
OL,7, an ex-partner who accused him of       
OL,8, "deceptively" transmitting HIV to him. 
OL,10,FIan Baum alleged Mr Thomas hid his HIV 
OL,11,Fstatus and "failed to take reasonable  
OL,12,Fcare" to ensure he did not pass it on. 
OL,14,FThe former British and Irish Lion said 
OL,15,Fhe had settled the case for #75,000    
OL,16,Fplus costs, but it was not an admission
OL,17,Fof liability or guilt.                 
OL,19,FMr Baum's lawyers confirmed a          
OL,20,Fsettlement had been agreed.            
